{"tid":2041904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Facebook 被駭 5 億用戶　香港 290 萬個私隱資料被出售","createTime":"2020-05-29T13:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T04:35:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e591720f1c1ec3232acab2c20eb952167a4821","tid":2041904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"Facebook 的用戶安全問題在過去多年一直為人詬病，多次傳出用戶資料外洩的它在近日更是再受醜聞的影響。據外國網站 Hack Read 最新發表的文章中提及，在上個月於 Dark web 出售的 2.67 億個 Facebook 用戶數據目前已經轉移至一個黑客論壇上出售，當中香港就有 290 萬名 Facebook 用戶的資料牽涉在內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/hacker-selling-500-million-facebook-user-data-1-1280x706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhacker-selling-500-million-facebook-user-data-1-1280x706.jpg&h=27bc419d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據外國網站 Hack Read 在最新的文章中指出，繼上個月有黑客於 Dark web 上出售 2.67 億名 Facebook 用戶數據後，目前該批數據已經轉移至一個黑客論壇上出售，當中不少用戶資料如姓名、位置、實際工作、婚姻狀況、手提電話號碼以及電子郵件地址亦可購買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而根據該出售的名單上，當中就有約 290 萬名香港的用戶資料亦可購買，而台灣及中國則分別有 73 萬及 67 萬的用戶均被列入名單當中。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/hacker-selling-500-million-facebook-user-data-2-1280x595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fhacker-selling-500-million-facebook-user-data-2-1280x595.jpg&h=52ff7b9c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/29/the-entire-database-is-being-sold-for-30000-on-a-hacker-forum/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F29%2Fthe-entire-database-is-being-sold-for-30000-on-a-hacker-forum%2Flife-tech%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33FKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=b685e6ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/29/the-entire-database-is-being-sold-for-30000-on-a-hacker-forum/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"5393d99910aba1fdce5bda4fea31cd5cd984f493","tid":2041904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"據該網站的透露，這批黑客將是次出售的數據分為三部分，當中每一百萬名用戶則收費 1,500 美元、每 10 萬用戶 450 美元以及每 5億名用戶 30,000 美元。該名單中更清楚指出，數據庫中的所有資訊均在 2019 年 11 月至 2020 年 5 月期間盜取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。據悉，目前全球多達最少有五億名用戶受事件影響。"},{"pid":"dbc4849a7cafd8792809a81cedefcc319cfc79ba","tid":2041904,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"即刻改密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484748f11defe53e79519f9fa346a117b5c7ea9a","tid":2041904,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"冇申請FB冇所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37001cec9eb00c85ad94a5b82377cf826f168f3","tid":2041904,"uid":198800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"0.0"},{"pid":"411112b86556935947dee444cf74bd01d0f506cd","tid":2041904,"uid":59586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"似就咁爬返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d157ee30f5cf39a9574950bc51afb09e8cc08df7","tid":2041904,"uid":60120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":